    # ── STYLE OBSERVATION 2: Question-first rhetorical structure ─
    narr:StyleObs_QuestionFirstRhetoric
      a narr:StyleObservation ;
      skos:broader narr:RhetoricalQuestion ;
      dct:source narr:Sample_WorksFromWhatWasSaid_20260610 ;
      skos:note "The deck's rhetorical architecture is built entirely on questions before any capability claim. The turn slide mirrors the three discovery questions in order — a structural anaphora that closes the loop. The close line ('Next call, I'll show you this conversation — turned into the beginning of your perspective') is a future-tense promise that makes the prospect the subject of the demo." ;
